<div class="thumb tright">
<div class="thumbinner" style="width:182px;"><a href="/wiki/File:Chemical_agent_protection.jpg" class="image" title="A Swedish Army soldier wearing a chemical agent protective suit (C-vätskeskydd) and his protection mask (skyddsmask 90)."><img alt="" src="http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/1/18/Chemical_agent_protection.jpg/180px-Chemical_agent_protection.jpg" width="180" height="240" border="0" class="thumbimage" /></a>
<div class="thumbcaption">
