<li id="cite_note-Ciottone2007-9"><b><a href="#cite_ref-Ciottone2007_9-0" title="">^</a></b> <cite style="font-style:normal" class="" id="CITEREFCiottoneArnold2007">Ciottone, Gregory R; Arnold, Jeffrey L (January 4, 2007), "<a href="http://www.emedicine.com/emerg/TOPIC852.HTM" class="external text" title="http://www.emedicine.com/emerg/TOPIC852.HTM" rel="nofollow">CBRNE - Chemical Warfare Agents</a>", <i>EMedicine</i><span class="printonly">, <a href="http://www.emedicine.com/emerg/TOPIC852.HTM" class="external free" title="http://www.emedicine.com/emerg/TOPIC852.HTM" rel="nofollow">http://www.emedicine.com/emerg/TOPIC852.HTM</a></span><span class="reference-accessdate">, retrieved on 2007-10-22</span></cite><span class="Z3988" title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Ajournal&amp;rft.genre=article&amp;rft.atitle=CBRNE+-+Chemical+Warfare+Agents&amp;rft.jtitle=EMedicine&amp;rft.aulast=Ciottone&amp;rft.aufirst=Gregory+R&amp;rft.au=Ciottone%2C+Gregory+R&amp;rft.au=Arnold%2C+Jeffrey+L&amp;rft.date=January+4%2C+2007&amp;rft_id=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.emedicine.com%2Femerg%2FTOPIC852.HTM&amp;rfr_id=info:sid/en.wikipedia.org:Chemical_warfare"><span style="display: none;">&#160;</span></span></li>
